  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK249">
<l>teruḷātāṉ meypporuḷ kaṇṭaṟṟāṟ ṟēṟi</l>
<l>ṉaruḷātāṉ ceyyu maṟam</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you consider, the virtue of him who is without kindness is like the perception of the true being by him who is without wisdom.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
